    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Symptom",
      "uuid": "a692b85bc15b4be3ab4d12587a1d1229",
      "x": 66836.49258146867,
      "y": 16448.097096317637,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 128.0,
      "z_value": -9.25900000000041,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Immediate removeItem during event processing caused 0xc0000005 \u2014 Qt's C++ internals weren't ready for re-entrant scene modification."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Root cause",
      "uuid": "a1aa5fcd8945423aaab56a703777f277",
      "x": 100047.30309648662,
      "y": 32876.876337060574,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 114.0,
      "z_value": -9.0990000000005,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Two interacting faults in the 2026-04-16 canonical _demolition_pre pattern:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "bb9fe66ae27248879144fbe6825916c4",
      "x": 42960.01193482315,
      "y": 17548.74281773604,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.515000000000269,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "So we don't actually train speed, we train per component towards precision, and it's through that precision that the overall becomes faster per iteration while becoming more precise rather than lose focus at speed."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Final state of _dismiss_loading_node()",
