      "z_value": -9.462000000000298,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "You said: \"same principle at every scale\"\n\"same principle at every scale\"\n-space rocket spends most of its life cycle not going fast at all until you light it up\n-Usain bolt isn't fast at all while going to 7-11, until it comes time to race"
    },
