    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "7133e861da084184b67f3ef28095904b",
      "x": 45126.080047974305,
      "y": 18655.5535326057,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.501000000000277,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Show more\nApr 27\nClaude responded: Yes \u2014 and this is the cleanest possible demonstration of the principle, because it happened in observable conditions with measurable outputs, and the failure m\u2026\nYes \u2014 and this is the cleanest possible demonstration of the principle, because it happened in observable conditions with measurable outputs, and the failure mode of the imitators is exactly what the theory predicts."
    },
