      "body_text": "1 Moved _is_emoji above the class definition Proper module-level helper, defined before first use\n2 Removed # \u2500\u2500 PrettyEdit (continued) comment Eliminated the false impression that methods below were inside the class\n3 paintEvent, _paint_selection_bg, _lift_view_focus, _restore_view_focus now inside class body AST confirms 15 methods on PrettyEdit (was 11)"
