      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "My recommendation: start with #1 \u2014 it's the housekeeping match for the morning's For Enjoying / randomling work and directly honours your drift-as-signal rule. If energy holds, #2 is a natural follow-on (same file, also tidy, no behavioural change). #3 wants a Pretty Widgets discussion, save it."
