      "label": "All three imports updated. The old file can stay or be deleted \u2014 nothing references it anymore. Let me also check `cozy-tree.txt` isn't an import:\n\nThat `cozy-tree.txt` reference is just documentation, not an import \u2014 harmless.\n\nDone. `utils/motivationalMessages.py` \u2192 `utils/PhrasePicker.py`, all three call sites (`main_window.py`, `AboutNodeData.py`, `WarmNodeData.py`) now import from the new name.",
      "depth_front": false,
