    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Inner Peace",
      "uuid": "f7267791cc8f4463833131ed6c146b9e",
      "x": 50459.38447138651,
      "y": -5141.288221887588,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 184.0,
      "z_value": -8.920000000000599,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "1. Header drift (the obvious one) \u2014 both Line 1s still say Intricate nodal playground (the pre-rename legacy), and the Line 2s read workmanlike rather than singing. Per your \"drift is the audit signal\" rule, the headers are themselves the cue to audit these files. Lowest risk, ends the symmetry with the morning's compliance work nicely."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "df8653cd46184e41b8f3bb1c3f2deab2",
      "x": 31694.419859745944,
      "y": 9483.457255379368,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.589000000000228,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Risk mitigation per node \u2014 added to the Phase 1 applicator"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "280a440983954ca3a44f006db9fd4c77",
      "x": 99586.5447350231,
      "y": 34526.10501374264,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 184.0,
      "z_value": -9.085000000000507,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "BaseNode._removal_done (added 2026-04-16) prevents _prepare_for_removal() from running twice. It is set to True at the top of _prepare_for_removal() and checked in itemChange before calling it. This makes teardown idempotent \u2014 safe for paths where a node is neutralized before the deferred removeItem fires."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Sweep",
      "uuid": "506f80eaf8864806bba5856dc210d48d",
      "x": 99418.63752692401,
      "y": 31750.116363269823,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 170.0,
      "z_value": -9.105000000000496,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Three files use QMediaPlayer in nodes/: VideoNode.py (canonical, 2026-04-16), AudioNode.py (this fix, 2026-04-20), MergeNode.py (subscribes to peer mediaStatusChanged only; already disconnects in its own _demolition_pre). No outstanding holes."
    },
    {
