      "body_text": "there is also documentation on the current state of the warmnode in ./Documents/Nodes/Warm Node , good to read up on that as well before we get started, as well as the stem of the idea for this round is to have a look into ./Documents/Nodes/Markdown node, and examine all the elaborate things it does while splitting up .md files for readability, and see which methodologies from that we can apply to the auto-splitting mechanism of the warm node."
