      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "- viewport-tracking signals (viewTransformed, scrollbar valueChanged) on pinned nodes\n- JoyStatsNode's 1-second _poll_timer.timeout \u2192 _refresh\n- ValueNode's _slider.valueChanged if the user is mid-scrub"
    },
    {
