      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Per the 2026-04-20 checklist addition, grep'd the node directory for QMediaPlayer usage: VideoNode (this fix), AudioNode (this fix \u2014 same commit), MergeNode (only subscribes to peer mediaStatusChanged, unaffected \u2014 its _demolition_pre already handles its own disconnects). Both media-owning siblings patched in the same commit this time."
