      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Format-agnostic ports from MarkdownNode (the green candidates)\nThings in MarkdownNode's pipeline that are already format-blind and would land on raw-text input as-is:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
