      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "But this was different\nA societal collapse thing\n\nA mission to get across the city that was in ruins\nGet some materials and stop the bad guy\n\nSuper fun, won the game and woke up.\nBut it reminded me of a clash\nBetween Hunger Games and the City of Lost Children\nIn a Strange day setting..."
