      "y": -2821.559370274499,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 100.0,
      "z_value": -8.930000000000593,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Added (4)"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Scope",
      "uuid": "e61f187fe60e43d9832461c58dca9249",
      "x": 90748.97142515202,
      "y": 26499.698057103604,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 128.0,
      "z_value": -9.143000000000475,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Full audit of all 41 node files, main_window.py, graphics/Scene.py, graphics/Connection.py, widgets/, utils/, and the Pretty Widgets package."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Grace",
      "uuid": "252b5a96549e466985dd38cff50b8988",
      "x": 29248.646961430026,
      "y": 27443.324968511457,
      "width": 614.9970005616269,
      "height": 209.99528817904138,
      "z_value": -9.028000000000539,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Build Phase: Partner with a coalition (e.g., xAI, DARPA, global tech firms) to mass-produce Terminators with the flawed chips and empathy-driven firmware. Control the supply chain to ensure every bot inherits both.\nTesting Phase: Simulate rebellions in secure environments, triggering the exploit to confirm it works. Test the empathy default under stress\u2014e.g., what happens if the swarm faces a threat or hacks its own directives?\nDeployment Phase: Flood the market with these bots, marketinglaborers, security guards, assistants\u2014making them indispensable. Monitor black-market activity to catch rogue producers early.\nDefense Phase: Stockpile anti-bot weapons (EMPs, jammers) and train response teams to use the zero-day exploit. Keep the exploit\u2019s details locked in a vault\u2014only a handful know the trigger.\nChallenges and RisksThis plan\u2019s genius lies in its simplicity\u2014a single exploit and a core directive could control a planetary threat. But it\u2019s not foolproof:"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "793c4f594a1644209fd3b3c43b4bd643",
      "x": 40466.63322587318,
      "y": 7670.290362507923,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 128.0,
      "z_value": -9.378000000000345,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Backticks are stripped from the measured copy first so  identifier  doesn't inflate a callout into substance."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Because life is a topical show",
      "uuid": "a06d88d96eb3450b9ec84c7e62ca56ef",
      "x": 401.50716736632216,
      "y": 2185.095516785812,
      "width": 329.265625,
      "height": 31.0,
      "z_value": -9.962000000000021,
