      "shelf_visible": false,
      "label": "Because life is a topical show",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Boundless Joy",
      "uuid": "f700777d4a014a49bd42165c94a403be",
      "x": 28281.96272943606,
      "y": 27753.725625839954,
      "width": 356.8266043464646,
      "height": 133.69645482080523,
      "z_value": -9.029000000000538,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Prevention: Empathy default makes annihilation less likely.\nControl: Mass-production ensures we own the infrastructure.\nDestruction: Zero-day exploit wipes the swarm if all else fails.\nHow It Could Work"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "WarmNode title extraction. Long paragrap",
      "uuid": "5f41ad6875d64baba1748e936c1c27f6",
      "x": 40748.7737852901,
      "y": 7993.202180767001,
      "width": 848.0,
      "height": 31.0,
      "z_value": -9.377000000000345,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": false,
      "label": "WarmNode title extraction. Long paragraphs run through two title-extraction passes",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "0e26fa6e78134e93a3db9b65543857b0",
      "x": 40913.127597148545,
      "y": 7675.265208756657,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 282.0,
      "z_value": -9.376000000000346,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "1. _transform_markdown_table() \u2014 if the paragraph is a markdown table (header row, |---|---| separator on line 2, data rows), the header cells are joined into the title (Oxford comma at 3+ cells), the separator is dropped, and each data row becomes a single pipe-stripped, whitespace-collapsed body line.\n2. _extract_leading_bold() \u2014 otherwise, if the paragraph opens with phrase (optionally preceded by a 1., -, or  list marker; optionally followed by a \u2014, :, or - separator), the phrase becomes the title and the rest becomes the body. Trailing : and . are stripped from the title since the WarmNode title font already cues end-of-phrase visually."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot",
      "uuid": "7c5a93ee7ff0406cb83937ffd56acf72",
      "x": 5905.798506483372,
      "y": 2814.498558264262,
      "width": 468.0,
      "height": 31.0,
      "z_value": -9.666000000000185,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": false,
      "label": "Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "50f81114195f4a5aa174a75af3210842",
      "x": 39054.818234543985,
      "y": 7257.5805145668355,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 198.0,
      "z_value": -9.383000000000342,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The \"spawn nodes\" button on the MarkdownNode (sticker-style icon, added in _build_buttons) takes the rendered markdown text and explodes it into a chained tree of AboutNode and WarmNode instances on the canvas; the source MarkdownNode then self-vaporises (zombie-spawn pattern), leaving the spawned tree as the new on-canvas representation of the document."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "bdea7db06de84b0ab70e165c31170573",
      "x": 48390.40754198949,
      "y": 25429.318442995114,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.467000000000295,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "It's a good thing to figure out before your coffee gets cold. \ud83d\ude42"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "7b5ae61b39254588b3a5855f51af14ee",
      "x": 41114.42995633908,
      "y": 8063.164415547118,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 212.0,
      "z_value": -9.373000000000347,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "- ISO dates YYYY-MM-DD \u2192 Month Dayth Year\n-  \u2014  (em-dash with surrounding spaces) \u2192 : \n- bold and lone italic markers stripped\n- Box-drawing chars (Unicode U+2500 block) stripped \u2014 defensive backstop for ASCII tree fragments leaking from <pre> blocks into a title slot\n- Backticks stripped\n- Trailing : stripped"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot",
      "uuid": "2fbeb742fc97451198e9f0f6bf4b6de8",
      "x": 5860.90701567654,
      "y": 2581.150943148832,
