      "body_text": "\"_split_oversized_paste constant cleanup \"\n  makes sense, as long as the graphics.Connection and utils.placement remain the canonical helper modules, they are both external modules so we can call them from anywhere and only ever update a single location to adjust the patterns of all the different places inside or out of intricate where we invoke those."
