      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.44200000000031,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "\"\"\"\nThey exist to demonstrate, by their accelerating decline, that the principle is real and that the laws underwriting it are not negotiable\n\"\"\"\n  Print on t-shirt worthy quote you just stated there."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intentional",
      "uuid": "f96a503abd124aa58837650b777d6979",
      "x": 10784.581531164036,
      "y": 530.8316719393074,
      "width": 313.783682547785,
      "height": 173.8736450354091,
      "z_value": -9.989000000000006,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "It's a terrible name for a parable\nSince there are so many 1-2-3 rules in this world\nAnd it even uses base numbers for identifiers\nBut the message in it is solid\nAnd we named it this in a hurry\nSo we are sticking to it\nAnd just going to go with it"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intricate",
      "uuid": "f5d47744118845b18ee7d31538e57f1a",
      "x": 10607.084414900837,
      "y": 2151.308733915356,
      "width": 307.38912893931604,
      "height": 226.06448077781738,
      "z_value": -9.972000000000016,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The two in this case\nAnd as per all the other terrible namings in this parable has nothing to do with other representative usages of a one, or a Two, or Threes or anything of the sort\n\nThe two in this case, with that mental image in your mind.\n\nIs the transfer of understanding\nfrom my context to yours"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Tiny little extra sprinkles of joy",
      "uuid": "3dab5b6827464cf9912086b488b89dab",
      "x": 10383.600878032234,
      "y": 2431.406656005542,
      "width": 379.25867288188175,
      "height": 108.470584768153,
      "z_value": -9.970000000000017,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The four then being the transfer of understanding\nfrom your context to The Five"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "b962f5038755491e863e98e2fdc32a1f",
      "x": 10830.055283221966,
      "y": 3021.6444126799347,
      "width": 354.3647440371416,
      "height": 117.9693696240729,
      "z_value": -9.966000000000019,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "They both carry the same default lexicon of understanding\nAnd interpretations through life"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "3d23c0f42f8a463fa29f9c713c1963c5",
      "x": 40869.676997371935,
      "y": 16148.242100994015,
      "width": 327.31769331630494,
      "height": 212.29399175132312,
      "z_value": -9.533000000000259,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The training period itself was a Phase 1 application on yourself. You ran the chain on the question of \"is installing this reflex worth the elaborate effort\" before committing \u2014 historical vs. potential of your own cognition, gain vs. effort vs. risk of the rewiring, singleton multiplier on whether your own mental environment justified the investment. The framework qualified its own installation. That's the cleanest possible proof that it works, because if it didn't, you'd have aborted partway through."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Endless Potential",
      "uuid": "b264a420edb44f378ab3810a744facb0",
      "x": 10452.766107247127,
      "y": 637.2026947450645,
      "width": 292.4603767279994,
      "height": 134.365506158776,
      "z_value": -9.987000000000007,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The most terrible thing about the name of this parable is the fact it doesn't even reference a linear thing then, as one would to be the suggestive title of naming it 1-2-3-4-5"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Note",
      "uuid": "fe135615a0ff405d97859ebe8185e4db",
      "x": 15275.585171626804,
      "y": 7040.045271529957,
      "width": 197.0,
