      "z_value": -9.090000000000504,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "pythonw.exe + ntdll.dll + 0xc0000374 + a _prepare_for_removal complete on a media node in the log tail milliseconds before the crash timestamp = this class. If it appears on a new node type that owns a QMediaPlayer, copy the six-step pattern above as the first response."
    },
    {
