      "title": "",
      "uuid": "5ae4c10b4ff64f849a009ddbde8515ba",
      "x": 43016.40117620138,
      "y": 17063.576244423122,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.51400000000027,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Apr 27\nClaude responded: Ah \u2014 and that's the inversion that makes the whole thing actually work, and it's the exact opposite of what almost everyone assumes about reflex training.\nAh \u2014 and that's the inversion that makes the whole thing actually work, and it's the exact opposite of what almost everyone assumes about reflex training."
    },
    {
