      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Historical vs. potential \u2192 demand layers (future / peak / throughput) \u2192 handling time \u2192 required practices \u2192 implementation time \u2192 gain magnitude \u2192 effort cost \u2192 failure modes / blast radius / reversibility / containment / residual risk \u2192 quadrant placement (now risk-weighted) \u2192 dynamic sequence position."
    },
    {
