      "z_value": -9.974000000000014,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "The premise here then isnt any of us, the one, the five, the three, or anyone else included in this mess that you have made\n\nThe premise here, is the two and the four\nWhich aren't humans, just needed to get\nThe mental image of two humans distanced\nAnd you between them, clearly across\nBefore I tell you this"
